    CTEXT "RuTTY \251 2013 Ernst Dijk.", IDA_TEXT2, 10, 30, 194, 8
    CTEXT "PuTTY \251 1997-2013 Simon Tatham.", IDA_TEXT2, 10, 38, 194, 8
